{"tid":957887,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎回到黑鏡第五季！互動式《黑鏡》最新預告曝光，明天就上線！","createTime":"2018-12-27T10:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T16:10:20.000Z","uid":41343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88dd5a13334c850ee34204878d77504039d248d2","tid":957887,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:59:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IDwfL5vmIZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIDwfL5vmIZA&d=FVM6g6NACJYo7aJBQQ6zKBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=13ed5042\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IDwfL5vmIZA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎回到《黑鏡》！大家最愛的黑科技神劇《黑鏡Black Mirror》第五季居然在2018年結束前回歸了！真是最好的跨年禮物（活動）啊，剛剛Netflix搶先曝光了《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基Black Mirror: Bandersnatch》正式預告，第五季黑鏡在12/28（是的也就是明天）就會上線。據國外消息指出《黑鏡Black Mirror》不會是影集形式，而可能會是獨立電影，會使用互動式劇集或獨立電影方式，片段則是長達5小時，觀眾可以根據劇情走向，自行決定主角將會走向如何的結局。<br />\n<br />\n不少媒體都報導，看起來是獨立電影的《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》》片長有可能會超過5個小時，或許是因為互動式內容讓每個結果都要拍，才讓總片長長度增加。最新曝光的《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》找來《敦克爾克大行動Dunkirk》受到矚目的主角包括 Fionn Whitehead、Will Poulter和 Asim Chaudhry 飾演。本季由導演David Slade執導，劇情回到了1984 年，一位年輕的程式設計師將一部情節複雜的奇幻小說改編成電玩，但擾人心智的挑戰隨即而來，他因此開始對現實產生質疑。"},{"pid":"b2abbacac493c2555e9b3772f7f1d07249652c33","tid":957887,"uid":160147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:01:34.000Z","msg":"正呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57066c7b84f1ee4bb21d438f26d3ffca58a6aea","tid":957887,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"7bbfb2d5a00960919758e9aa6fb0f84b82bb19de","tid":957887,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d94e976229342208872137a9963e0c75360fd7","tid":957887,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s